name: Can I have a piece of Green Cake ?
description:
I live in a tropical country where there are a lot of trees. I love living in my cold and sunny country. While on the other side of my country there is a fire in a vast tropical forest that has consumed more than 1000 trees. Through this artwork, I want to remind you not to do any harm in the forest. Forests, trees, and other creatures were created for a reason.

peace...
